data.description: This beautiful triplex in the heart of Echo Park is listed for sale for the first time in 30 years!     All units have their own separate entrances. The front building has 2 units (one is upstairs). A 3rd unit is a detached unit with its own entrance and 2 different parking spaces accessible from the next street on Ashmore Place. The length of this lot stretches from Echo Park Ave to Ashmore Place (see the image of the parcel map).  The property is a landbank (5357 sq/ft) perfect for owner-user with rental income, investment property, or for future development. Unit 1804 is owner-occupied so there is an upside in rent (only unit 1804 will be delivered vacant). It is only a 5-minute drive to Dodger Stadium, within walking distance to Lady Byrd Cafe and nearby restaurants. There's also a mini market directly across the street from the property. Please do not disturb tenants.
